tion_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572994232"&gt;6月26日thur早上期指及恒指趨勢update:&lt;br&gt;昨晚夜期收24326跌144點。美股三大指數漲跌不一，標普500指數接近歷史高點。美聯儲主席鮑威爾再次重申不急於降息，強調高關稅帶來很大的不確定性。截至收盤，道指跌106.59點，跌幅爲0.25%，報42982.43點；納指漲61.02點，漲幅爲0.31%，報19973.55點；今天恒生指數24400水位整固。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31966466&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1076156129685c9b5ea79ef4_79184493"/><published>2025-06-26T08:26:00+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>5db146e0f3f89bdc7d72b5427616c388</id><title>今年先升後跌，高位已出。。</title><updated>2025-06-26T08:30:29+08:00</updated><author><name>流西水股</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-26T08:30:29+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572994284"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572994284"&gt;立帖為証&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="58" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_47.gif"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="4" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/cry.gif"/&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31966471&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1076156129685c9b5ea79ef4_79184493"/><published>2025-06-26T08:30:29+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>ca87146c8c4c4f5a30226bc446bd3bee</id><title>美國以色列北韓都可以擁有核武。。</title><updated>2025-06-26T08:34:19+08:00</updated><author><name>流西水股</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-26T08:34:19+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572994330"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572994330"&gt